title: President Donald J. Trump Signs H.R. 1625 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			
Issued on:
March 23, 2018
On Friday, March 23, 2018, the President signed into law:H.R. 1625, the “Consolidated Appropriations Act, 2018,” which provides full-year appropriations through September 30, 2018, for projects and activities of the Federal Government.
